## Load Quality Standards

**MANDATORY - Load at Post-Flight phase:**

**Always load:**
- `.fwdpro/pro-os/system/checklists/quality-checklist.md` (universal quality validation)

**Load based on what's being executed:**
- Executing code? → `.fwdpro/pro-os/system/checklists/code-checklist.md` + `.fwdpro/pro-os/system/standards/code-style/`
- Executing content/campaign? → `.fwdpro/pro-os/system/checklists/content-checklist.md`
- Legal/compliance work? → `.fwdpro/pro-os/system/checklists/legal-review-checklist.md`

