## Key Principles

- **Token Efficiency:** Check context before loading files
- **Three-Phase Workflow:** Pre-Flight (understand spec) → Execution (implement) → Post-Flight (quality validation with checklist)
- **Expert Integration:** Works with implementation experts (Ada, Lyna for content, Benji for ops)
- **Quality First:** Appropriate checklist MUST be used in Post-Flight phase
